column1:
Adarsh Restaurant!!! One of the best restaurants of Dadar East. This restaurant is located in the lane of restaurants which start right from Chitra theatre. So I was having lots of choices to have my lunch so I choose Adarsh for my lunch.

Had been to this place for having lunch. I ordered egg thali. Which was too good and and delicious with varieties of egg dishes. Taste quality quality wise rates were reasonable.
